WEBVTT

00:00.680 --> 00:02.160
With my meager virtue

00:02.440 --> 00:04.080
I have reigned for 27 years

00:04.760 --> 00:07.320
Worries accumulated in my heart, working diligently without rest

00:07.840 --> 00:10.160
Fearing I would fail the ancestral foundation

00:11.560 --> 00:12.880
Now the realm is settled

00:13.480 --> 00:14.480
The divine land recovered

00:15.360 --> 00:16.560
I am gravely ill

00:17.040 --> 00:18.320
And cannot rise

00:18.320 --> 00:19.600
This is the natural way of life and death

00:20.040 --> 00:21.640
Unavoidable for all people, past and present

00:22.280 --> 00:23.840
You need not lament

00:24.640 --> 00:26.160
Marquis of Yongning Xie Xuan

00:26.800 --> 00:29.520
Pillar of the state, loyalty shines like sun and moon

00:30.280 --> 00:33.600
In the future, he may be the first among your advisors

00:34.480 --> 00:36.120
The succession has found the right person

00:36.400 --> 00:38.160
The ancestral temple and people have someone to rely on

00:38.680 --> 00:40.320
Though I depart this world

00:41.000 --> 00:43.320
What regrets do I have?
